  "content": {
    "problemStatement": "<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Synonyms are words or phrases that have the same, or nearly the same, meaning as another word or phrase in the same language.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Using synonyms in writing helps to create richer text by conveying different degrees of meaning. Additionally, it's a great way to add variations to your writing and avoid repeating the same words over and over again.\u00a0</span></p><h3 id=\"few-examples-of-synonyms-are-given-below\" style=\"text-align:left\"><span>Few Examples of Synonyms are given below:</span></h3><h4 id=\"synonyms-for-beautiful\" style=\"text-align:left\"><span>Synonyms for Beautiful:</span></h4><blockquote><ul><li value=\"1\"><span>Alluring</span></li><li value=\"2\"><span>Appealing</span></li><li value=\"3\"><span>Charming\u00a0</span></li><li value=\"4\"><span>Stunning</span></li><li value=\"5\"><span>Dazzling</span></li></ul></blockquote><h4 id=\"synonyms-for-happy\" style=\"text-align:left\"><span>Synonyms for Happy:</span></h4><blockquote><ul><li value=\"1\"><span>Cheerful\u00a0</span></li><li value=\"2\"><span>Contented </span></li><li value=\"3\"><span>Delighted\u00a0</span></li><li value=\"4\"><span>Ecstatic\u00a0</span></li><li value=\"5\"><span>Elated</span></li></ul></blockquote><h4 id=\"synonyms-for-amazing\" style=\"text-align:left\"><span>Synonyms for Amazing:</span></h4><blockquote><ul><li value=\"1\"><span>Astounding\u00a0</span></li><li value=\"2\"><span>Incredible</span></li><li value=\"3\"><span>Breathtaking\u00a0</span></li><li value=\"4\"><span>Extraordinary\u00a0</span></li><li value=\"5\"><span>Impressive</span></li></ul></blockquote><h4 id=\"synonyms-for-good\" style=\"text-align:left\"><span>Synonyms for Good:</span></h4><blockquote><ul><li value=\"1\"><span>Acceptable</span></li><li value=\"2\"><span>Excellent</span></li><li value=\"3\"><span>Exceptional</span></li><li value=\"4\"><span>Favorable</span></li><li value=\"5\"><span>Great</span></li></ul></blockquote><h4 id=\"synonyms-for-love\" style=\"text-align:left\"><span>Synonyms for Love:</span></h4><blockquote><ul><li value=\"1\"><span>Admiring</span></li><li value=\"2\"><span>Affectionate</span></li><li value=\"3\"><span>Fondness</span></li><li value=\"4\"><span>Adoration</span></li><li value=\"5\"><span>Devotion</span></li></ul></blockquote><h4 id=\"synonyms-for-sad\" style=\"text-align:left\"><span>Synonyms for Sad:</span></h4><blockquote><ul><li value=\"1\"><span>Sorrowful</span></li><li value=\"2\"><span>Dismal</span></li><li value=\"3\"><span>Heartbroken</span></li><li value=\"4\"><span>Melancholy</span></li><li value=\"5\"><span>Mournful\u00a0</span></li></ul></blockquote><h4 id=\"synonyms-for-great\" style=\"text-align:left\"><span>Synonyms for Great:</span></h4><blockquote><ul><li value=\"1\"><span>Excellent</span></li><li value=\"2\"><span>Magnificent</span></li><li value=\"3\"><span>Fine</span></li><li value=\"4\"><span>Glorious</span></li><li value=\"5\"><span>Grand\u00a0</span></li></ul></blockquote><h4 id=\"synonyms-for-show\" style=\"text-align:left\"><span>Synonyms for Show:</span></h4><blockquote><ul><li value=\"1\"><span>Display</span></li><li value=\"2\"><span>Exhibit</span></li><li value=\"3\"><span>Unveil</span></li><li value=\"4\"><span>Reveal</span></li><li value=\"5\"><span>Demonstrate</span></li></ul></blockquote><h3 id=\"also-check\" style=\"text-align:left\"><b><strong>Also Check:</strong></b></h3><blockquote><p dir=\"ltr\"><span>\u27a3 Synonyms Solved Question- </span><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude-synonyms-solved-questions-and-answers\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Refer Here</span></a><span>! </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>\u27a3 Test your knowledge- </span><a href=\"https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/quizzes/synonyms/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Quiz</span></a><span>!</span></p></blockquote>",
